headline: 2 Internet Stocks on Our Watchlist and 1 to Turn Down
summary: By breaking down physical barriers, consumer internet businesses are reshaping how people shop, connect, learn, and play. Luckily for them, the market seems to believe there is a long runway for growth as the industry has recorded a 3.7% gain over the past six months while the S&P 500 was stuck in neutral.
